### Statistics API Endpoints

### Get Overview Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats/overview
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Category Statistics (All Categories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats/categories
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Category Statistics (Specific Categories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats/categories?categories=Fiction,Mystery,Romance&include_distribution=true
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Category Statistics (Specific Categories without Distribution)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats/categories?categories=Fiction,Poetry&include_distribution=false
Accept: {{contentType}}
